
 1. Anna pays Charlie 100 $
 - signs that transaction with her private key and a message insides,
 - this generates a hash number
 - this transaction that is markerd with her signature is putted on the ledger list of transcations,
 - every single transaction that she will make will be signed by a different signature,
 so that is why those signatures can not be used another time
 - signature of a transaction is always created on the user side,
 - publike key is used to verify that signature was created from a private key,